profile:
Coastal Energy is Vancouver Islandâ€™s heating and cooling experts. Located in Nanaimo, we offer installation and repair services to most of Central Vancouver Island, including Nanaimo, Ladysmith, Cedar, Parksville, Qualicum, Chemainus & Duncan.

We install, service and repair Ductless Heat Pumps, Gas Furnaces and Heat Pumps amongst other products.

Established in 2005, Coastal has grown from a 2 person operation to 8+ staff, multiple service vehicles and extended the territory in which it serves. We're very proud to say that our owners work "in the business" and you'll no doubt meet them if you're interested in receiving a quote.

profile: Local, family run business with five star service. Repairing and installing HVAC equipment for both residential and commercial locations. Specializing in Heat Pumps, both ducted and ductless, Gas furnaces, Hot Water Tanks and much more. Call today for a free quote on how you can run a more efficient heating and cooling system in your home. Our technicians are Red Seal Journeyman Refrigeration Mechanics with a combined experience of over 70 years installing, servicing and repairing all types of heat pumps in Canada, UK, Europe, the Middle East, and at least 2 Caribbean Islands as well - we know heat pumps!
